sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant UI as React Client
    participant SRV as Express Server
    participant FB as Firebase Auth
    participant DUO as Duo Security

    rect rgb(240, 240, 255)
        Note over U, DUO: 4. Login with Duo 2FA (when configured)
        U->>UI: Enters email & password
        UI->>SRV: POST /auth/login
        SRV-->>SRV: Verify password ✓
        SRV-->>UI: 200 {requiresDuo: true, duoState}
        UI-->>U: Redirect to Duo prompt
        U->>DUO: Complete Duo challenge<br/>(push notification or passcode)
        DUO-->>SRV: OIDC callback with auth code
        SRV->>DUO: Exchange code for token
        DUO-->>SRV: Duo verification token ✓
        SRV->>FB: signInWithEmailAndPassword()
        FB-->>SRV: Firebase ID token
        SRV-->>UI: 200 {token, user, role}
        UI-->>U: Redirect to Map View
    end

    rect rgb(248, 249, 250)
        Note over U, DUO: 5. Session Management & Role Switching
        UI->>SRV: GET /auth/me (on page load)
        Note right of SRV: Verify Firebase ID token<br/>via Authorization header
        SRV-->>UI: 200 {user, role, isAdmin}
        Note right of UI: Session stored in localStorage<br/>2-minute inactivity timeout<br/>Auto-logout on expiry
        U->>UI: Clicks role toggle
        UI->>SRV: POST /auth/role {userType: "bidder"}
        SRV-->>SRV: db.user.update(uid, {userType})
        SRV-->>UI: 200 {updated user}
        UI-->>UI: Update session & UI
    end
